####  You want some loan and a bank is ready to give you loan on simple interest. 
      It is given that when you will return the amount, you will return amount which 
      is twice of principal amount. Bank has given you rate R . You have to find the 
      time after which you will be returning the total amount
      
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
#include <math.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main() {

    float t;
    scanf("%f",&t);
    printf("%.2f",100/t);
    return 0;
}

